  <description>
    <p>
      Secrets is a modern password manager built with GTK4 and Libadwaita that provides
      a beautiful native interface for managing passwords stored with 'pass', the standard Unix password manager.
      It features an intelligent setup wizard, comprehensive password management capabilities, and
      a polished user experience designed for both casual users and power users.
    </p>
    <p>âœ¨ Modern Interface &amp; User Experience:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Beautiful GTK4/Libadwaita interface with adaptive design</li>
      <li>Comprehensive keyboard shortcuts for efficient navigation</li>
      <li>Real-time search with instant filtering</li>
      <li>Hierarchical folder organization with expandable tree view</li>
      <li>Import/Export functionality (JSON, CSV formats)</li>
      <li>Intelligent setup wizard with guided GPG and pass configuration</li>
    </ul>
    <p>ğŸ” Comprehensive Password Management:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Structured password entries with username, URL, notes, and custom fields</li>
      <li>Advanced password generator with strength indicators and customizable options</li>
      <li>TOTP (Time-based One-Time Password) support with live countdown timers</li>
      <li>Recovery codes management for 2FA backup and account recovery</li>
      <li>Smart clipboard management with automatic clearing</li>
      <li>Password visibility controls and secure display options</li>
    </ul>
    <p>ğŸ› ï¸ Setup &amp; Configuration:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Automatic GPG key detection and setup assistance</li>
      <li>Guided pass (password-store) installation and initialization</li>
      <li>Cross-platform compatibility (Linux with Flatpak support)</li>
      <li>Seamless integration with existing pass stores</li>
      <li>No manual terminal configuration required</li>
    </ul>
    <p>ğŸš€ Planned Features (Roadmap):</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Git synchronization with multi-platform support (GitHub, GitLab, Codeberg)</li>
      <li>Advanced security features and session management</li>
      <li>Automatic idle locking with configurable timeouts</li>
      <li>Failed attempt protection with lockout mechanisms</li>
      <li>Real-time Git status monitoring with visual indicators</li>
      <li>Repository setup wizard with platform API integration</li>
      <li>Enhanced automation and workflow improvements</li>
      <li>Master password timeout for periodic re-authentication</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

